    </p>
    <p class="w-3/4 py-10">
      This experience will refine your decision making abilities, enhance your situational awareness, and deepen your understanding of instrument flight operations. As you overcome the challenges of long distance flying, you will develop the confidence and competence required to navigate confidently through the instrument system and safely reach your destination.
    </p>
  </div>
